content: (maanavar vaanor mun mun nin... Enna pole)

Daivatthinnekan puthran-vaanatthattil ninnetthi
Vallabhanaam daivattheppol -kaanaavil cheythaashcharyam.
Veenyu virunninillennu -maathaa kartthaavodothi
Naaree! Maunam deekshikken-neram vannittillennaan.
Veenyu virunnil theernnappoll-kartthaavin kalpana pole
Bhrthyanmaar kalppaathrangall-vellllatthaal poorippichu
Srashdaavaam vijnyan vellllam-veenyaakki thoshippichu
Sarvvanmaarum kartthaavin-saujanyatthe keertthichu.
